<item>
            <title>[LU-12035] DoM/HSM: released file appears with &quot;unknown&quot; layout type</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12035</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If releasing a file striped on MDT, it appears with a lmm_pattern &quot;unknown&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
This may be a lack in liblustreapi&apos;s layout2name().&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# lfs hsm_release /mnt/lustre/domfile
# lfs getstripe /mnt/lustre/domfile
/mnt/lustre/domfile
 lcm_layout_gen: 3
 lcm_mirror_count: 1
 lcm_entry_count: 2
 lcme_id: 1
 lcme_mirror_id: 0
 lcme_flags: init
 lcme_extent.e_start: 0
 lcme_extent.e_end: 1048576
 lmm_stripe_count: 0
 lmm_stripe_size: 1048576
* lmm_pattern: unknown*
 lmm_layout_gen: 0
 lmm_stripe_offset: 0
lcme_id: 2
 lcme_mirror_id: 0
 lcme_flags: init
 lcme_extent.e_start: 1048576
 lcme_extent.e_end: EOF
 lmm_stripe_count: -1
 lmm_stripe_size: 4194304
 lmm_pattern: released
 lmm_layout_gen: 65535
 lmm_stripe_offset: 0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
